{"tid":648471,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"90's Telegram Group","createTime":"2018-04-30T16:54:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-08T14:15:39.000Z","uid":180125,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b4b4ac76f2fff2cd6ab282884da93f53d9409d8d","tid":648471,"uid":180125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T16:54:18.000Z","msg":"開左個TG Group. 有私隱得來其實都唔係話勁有私隱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n歡迎90後各行各業嘅各位一齊入來吹下水傾下計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我們希望關系和諧，因始沒有你我之分，更沒有兩登之分<br />\n<br />\n90's Telegram Group為會員而設，暫時只限相關會員加入<br />\n<br />\nGroup內比較著重繁體字及廣東話文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n麻煩填一填表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n表格會開到5月8日，填妥表格後會收到一封確認電郵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n*表格內有聲明及條款細則，根據過往經驗而定為左保障大家 希望大家睇一睇，而同意聲明及條款細則係要輸入電話號碼作確認. 此資料一般情況下絕不公開<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdDZQexPqevoT7eGySsf3Vc414udW3KMFa5cU0Fma30HLHOEw/viewform?usp=sf_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdDZQexPqevoT7eGySsf3Vc414udW3KMFa5cU0Fma30HLHOEw%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dsf_link&d=CKP6R7xOsIMcEqWMGR%2ByKHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=87ebfb66\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdDZQexPqevoT7eGySsf3Vc414udW3KMFa5cU0Fma30HLHOEw/viewform?usp=sf_link</a>"},{"pid":"3ce8593b39e7858683352c40e906b4dd6395c614","tid":648471,"uid":180125,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T17:14:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b1924234a13830ef446425fd55fe8f998b83e97","tid":648471,"uid":180125,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T01:44:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.